    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sun-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……まさか\nアイドル、辞めるつもりなんですか……？",
      "startTime": 2.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "――え？",
      "startTime": 4.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "サニピに、遙子さんよりふさわしい人なんていない",
      "startTime": 5.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんがいなかったら、サニピも月ストも\nここまで来ることは出来ませんでした",
      "startTime": 12.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "そう、なのかな",
      "startTime": 14.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "俺、今日言いましたよね。遙子さんはチームを\nまとめるのがうまいって。でも、撤回させて下さい",
      "startTime": 21.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "え……どうして……？\n私、うまく出来てなかった……？",
      "startTime": 28.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "アイドル、佐伯遙子の魅力はそれだけじゃないからです",
      "startTime": 31.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "は……はい？",
      "startTime": 35.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんはどんな時でも、自分より他の人を思いやって\n最高の笑顔とエールを贈れる、凄いアイドルです",
      "startTime": 41.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それにどれだけ元気をもらえたことか……\n俺だけじゃなく、サニピのみんなもファンもです",
      "startTime": 48.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうかな？　そんなに褒められると\nちょっと照れちゃうけど……",
      "startTime": 56.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "あと遙子さんの実力は、デビュー当時から本物でした\nきっかけさえあれば、絶対にブレイクしていました",
      "startTime": 63.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "そのきっかけが、サニーピースの結成だったと思うんだ\nだから私、凄く幸運だなって……",
      "startTime": 71.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "違う。幸運だったのは遙子さんじゃない\n他のみんなです",
      "startTime": 78.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どういう意味……？",
      "startTime": 79.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "デビュー経験のある遙子さんは\n唯一、プロの厳しさを知っていたアイドルでした",
      "startTime": 84.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "だから、他のみんなをフォローしたり\n先輩としてアドバイスを与えて、導いてきた",
      "startTime": 90.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとう。そんな風に言ってもらえて\n凄く嬉しいよ",
      "startTime": 96.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルとして最高の武器を持っている\n経験もあるし、まとめ役だってこなせる",
      "startTime": 101.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんはこんなものじゃない。もっと上を目指せる\nなのに、アイドルを辞めるなんて……",
      "startTime": 108.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "辞めないけど？",
      "startTime": 111.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "えっ",
      "startTime": 113.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "だから、辞めないわよ\nどうして私が辞める前提で話が進んでるの？",
      "startTime": 116.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "でも、「心が揺らいでる」とか\n「もっとふさわしい人がいる」とか言うから……",
      "startTime": 123.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "辞めるとは言ってないでしょ？\nここまで来たのにもったいないじゃない",
      "startTime": 129.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "それなら、もっと早く訂正して下さいよ……",
      "startTime": 131.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "ごめん。あまりに私の魅力を熱弁するから\nついついもうちょっと聞いていたくて……",
      "startTime": 141.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあさっき、「決めたの」の後に\nなんて言おうとしてたんですか？",
      "startTime": 147.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_03-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "……私、今日の今日まで、心のどこかで疑ってたの\nいつかみんなに置いて行かれちゃうんじゃないかって",
      "startTime": 156.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
